name: S21 Ultra
description: The Galaxy S21 Ultra has a cutting-edge flagship chipset. An Exynos 2100 and a Snapdragon 888 depending on the market. These processors are built on a 5nm process. The results, of the two chipsets both performance & graphics-wise, are outstanding. The phone performs real-world tasks smoothly providing a quality gaming experience. The device provides support for 5G network connectivity as well.  The Galaxy S21Ultra comes with the newer UFS 3.1 which has a faster transfer speed. The device comes in a variation of 12 GB of & 16 GB RAM. The user has three storage options to choose from. A 128 GB option, a 256 GB option & a 512 GB option. You don’t have the option of expandable storage anymore.  This new device supports Samsung One UI 3.1 based on Android 11. The Galaxy S21 Ultra model is built around a 6.8 inch dynamic AMOLED display with a small punch hole for the selfie camera The phone offers 1440 x 3200 pixels with a high QHD resolution. The S21 Ultra also offers a fast 120 Hz adaptive refresh rate.   One unique feature of the Galaxy S21 Ultra is that it supports an S-Pen stylus which before this could only be found in the Galaxy Note series.

name: Samsung Galaxy A02
description: The device is going to have a new look and design. Today two handsets got leaked are A02 and M02, but there are no specs details of the phones. Recently the device with model number SM-A025F, which is believed to have Samsung Galaxy A02 appeared on Geekbench. The fact that they have a single page in the Norwegian regulator's database indicates that Samsung's Galaxy A02 and Galaxy M02 are the same devices for different regions. As for the specs of the phone are concerned, the new smartphone will be powered by Mediatek MT6739W (28 nm) SoC which is a powerful chipset. The new Samsung Galaxy A02's having a 1.5 GHz Octa-Core processor inside. The smartphone coupled with 3 gigabytes of RAM, this quality of RAM is enough to run the functions of the smartphone smoothly. The upcoming handset of the company Galaxy A02 by Samsung has got 32 gigabytes of internal storage, which is not enough but there is a dedicated slot in this device that can supports up to 256 gigabytes. The Samsung A02 has got a triple camera setup. The main lens of the setup will be 13 megapixels along with a 13 megapixels ultra-wide shooter and a 2 megapixels depth lens to capture excellent photography. Samsung Galaxy's A02 is packed with an 5 megapixels front-selfie camera setup. The 6.5 inches display size, and IPS LCD panel will provide the phone with an HD resolution of 720 x 1520 Pixels. The new Samsung Galaxy A02 has the protection of Corning Gorilla Glass which will make this smartphone safer to use. The device has a 3.5mm Audio Jack that the users will be enjoying listing to the music. The new Galaxy A02's is a budget-friendly phone with outstanding features.

name: Samsung Galaxy A03s
description: The Samsung Galaxy A03s arrives as the successor to the Galaxy A02 phone which was also one of the best-selling Samsung phones in the world. The coming smartphone of the company which will be called Samsung's Galaxy A03s will be powered by one of the latest chipsets called a MediaTek Helio G35. This is a high-quality chipset that has been introduced in different brands. Samsung Galaxy A03s's going to have a 2.0 GHz Octa-Core processor to give more power to this chipset. If we talk about the display panel of the smartphone, it is equipped with 6.5 Inches display screen that will be full HD plus a resolution of 720 x 1600 Pixels, the users of this Galaxy A03s by Samsung will be happy to use this big screen. To protect this screen there is a Corning Gorilla Glass is installed. The coming device of this company, Samsung A03s is having 3 gigabytes of RAM to make the processing speed of the device lightning fast. The internal storage of the handset is 64 gigabytes which means that the Samsung Galaxy's A03s is providing the user with enough storage capacity to store data for the future. There is a also microSD card in this device. There is a dual rear camera setup in Samsung Galaxy A03s, The main sensor of the rear camera setup will be 13 megapixels wide, and a 2- Mega-pixel macro, and 2-Mega-pixel depth sensor. The handset is expected to come equipped with a 5 megapixels selfie shooter. For the security of user's data, the Galaxy A03s's got a side-mounted Fingerprint Sensor which is a normal feature nowadays on smartphones. The battery of this device is Li-Po Non-removable 5000 mAh with a 7.8W Battery charging.

name: Infinix Hot 11S
description: Infinix is launching its new Hot 11s on the market soon. The Chinese company Infinix is working on a new smartphone of its Hot-series, and it will be launched in mid of September this year. The coming smartphone will be the direct successor of Hot 10s. The upcoming device will be called Infinix Hot 11S. The chipset that is going to power the upcoming smartphone will be Helio G88. This is a powerful chipset that handsomely handles all the specs of mid-range smartphones. To give more power to this Infinix's Hot 11S, there is an Octa-Core processor installed under the hood of this handset. Also, the device has got a GPU of Mali-G52. The smartphone got the Capacitive IPS LCD Touchscreen display which is exclusively made for the devices of this brand. Infinix Hot 11S's going to have a full HD display with a resolution of 1080 x 2460 Pixels. Also, there is a big screen of 6.78 Inches. The SoC of the handset is paired with 4 gigabytes of RAM. The chipset and the RAM of the Hot 11S by Infinix will make the processing speed of the phone lightning fast. The internal storage capacity of the device is 128 gigabytes. This is enough storage capacity that will give you enough space to place a huge amount of data for future use. The Smartphone Infinix 11S has got a Triple Camera setup on the rear, the main camera will be 50 megapixels main camera and 2 megapixels, 2 megapixels lens. On the front-facing, there is an 8 megapixels selfie camera setup. The security of this Infinix Hot's 11S to protect your data it has a rear-mounted, optical fingerprint scanner. The phone is fueled with a powerful battery of 5000 mAh capacity. It means you can use the smartphone Infinix Hot 11S for a long period of time. And also there is an 18W of fast battery charging. This coming up new Hot 11S's will be a competitor of Samsung as the specs look quite impressive.

name: Infinix Smart 5 Pro
description: This Infinix Smart 5 Pro is an impressively inexpensive phone with a beautiful design and solid specs. The phone comes with a 6.52 Full FullHD + screen that has a 20:9 aspect ratio and a pixel density of 269ppi. Under the hood, this smartphone is powered by an Unisoc SC9863A (28nm) Soc chipset and comes with 4 GB of RAM. The phone comes with an Android 11 and XOS 7.6 user interface and has 32 GB of internal storage (ROM). This smartphone also has a microSD card slot for further memory expansion up to 256 GB. When it comes to cameras, this Infinix Smart 5 Pro has an 8 MP selfie camera, and on the back, there is a system of dual cameras, which includes the main sensor of 13 MP, and a secondary sensor of QVGA. In addition to the triple camera on the back and the Quad-LED flash, there is also a fingerprint scanner, and below it is the name of the company Infinix. When it comes to battery life, this smartphone comes with a 6000 mAh battery, and a 10W charger also comes in the sales package. You will charge the phone via the micro USB slot.
